rows.label: soul26_P0101
rows.name: Here we go! Melee attacks!

rows.label: soul26_P0102
rows.name:
A melee attack might
knock 'em for a loop!

rows.label: soul26_P0103
rows.name:
Let's thwack 'em and get
that blood pumpin'!

rows.label: soul26_P0201
rows.name: Blast 'em to bits!

rows.label: soul26_P0202
rows.name:
Let's buff up and
get in the zone!

rows.label: soul26_P0203
rows.name:
Maybe we should
weaken 'em first!

rows.label: soul26_P0301
rows.name:
Now! Devastate 'em
with a melee attack!

rows.label: soul26_P0302
rows.name: Take that! Fire at will!

rows.label: soul26_P0303
rows.name:
Use an aura and find
your groove!

rows.label: soul26_P0401
rows.name: I could use a heal here!

rows.label: soul26_P0402
rows.name:
Man, I'm bushed.
Help a girl out!

rows.label: soul26_P0403
rows.name:
I can get back in this!
Buff me up!

rows.label: soul26_P0501
rows.name: I'm dying here! Heal me!

rows.label: soul26_P0502
rows.name:
I don't wanna die!
Patch me up!

rows.label: soul26_P0503
rows.name:
Now! Buff up and
go mental on 'em!

rows.label: soul26_P0601
rows.name:
Move in and knock 'em
around...for me...

rows.label: soul26_P0602
rows.name:
Forget about me...
Just shoot 'em...

rows.label: soul26_P0603
rows.name:
I wish I could see
one last aura...

rows.label: soul26_P0701
rows.name: Bam! Now hit 'em!

rows.label: soul26_P0702
rows.name: Bam! Now shoot 'em!

rows.label: soul26_P0703
rows.name: Try crippling 'em!

rows.label: soul26_P0801
rows.name: Got it! Okay, now floor 'em!

rows.label: soul26_P0802
rows.name:
Knock 'em flat with
a ranged attack!

rows.label: soul26_P0803
rows.name: We can cripple 'em!

rows.label: soul26_P0901
rows.name:
They're flagging!
Mow 'em down!

rows.label: soul26_P0902
rows.name: Let's buff up and save time!

rows.label: soul26_P0903
rows.name:
Let's Overdrive right
over these guys!

rows.label: soul26_P1001
rows.name:
Finally! A chance to
smack 'em around!

rows.label: soul26_P1002
rows.name:
What are you waiting for?
Shoot 'em!

rows.label: soul26_P1003
rows.name: Now! Weaken 'em!

rows.label: soul26_P1101
rows.name:
Use an aura to
level things out!

rows.label: soul26_P1102
rows.name:
How about another aura
for good measure?

rows.label: soul26_P1103
rows.name:
Let's pick things up
with a buff!

rows.label: soul26_P1201
rows.name: Hop on the bandwagon!

rows.label: soul26_P1202
rows.name:
Overdrive! Let's go
nuts on 'em!

rows.label: soul26_P1203
rows.name: Cover me with an aura!

rows.label: soul26_C0101
rows.name:
Okay, get up close and
personal with the next one!

rows.label: soul26_C0102
rows.name:
Who's next? Let's hear
those guns roar!

rows.label: soul26_C0103
rows.name:
We're not done yet!
Buff up while you can!

rows.label: soul26_C0201
rows.name:
Ha, easy! Let's see
those auras!

rows.label: soul26_C0202
rows.name: Time to buff up!

rows.label: soul26_C0203
rows.name: Let's blast 'em!

rows.label: soul26_C0301
rows.name: Yeah! Now fry 'em up!

rows.label: soul26_C0302
rows.name: Look at me go! Now blast 'em!

rows.label: soul26_C0303
rows.name:
Did you SEE that?
Let's see you beat that!

rows.label: soul26_C0401
rows.name:
Guess the forecast
was wrong. Bundle up!

rows.label: soul26_C0402
rows.name:
I hate weather like this!
We should use auras!

rows.label: soul26_C0403
rows.name:
Forget the weather.
Just cripple the enemy!

rows.label: soul26_C0501
rows.name:
That's gotta be an intergalactic
record! We should celebrate!

rows.label: soul26_C0502
rows.name:
I'm bushed! How about
a little boost?

rows.label: soul26_C0503
rows.name:
Over here, you freak!
Perfect, now use Overdrive!

rows.label: soul26_C0601
rows.name:
Wow, thanks!
Go hit 'em for me!

rows.label: soul26_C0602
rows.name:
Wow, thanks!
Shoot 'em for me!

rows.label: soul26_C0603
rows.name:
Awww. Don't forget to protect
yourself with an aura!

rows.label: soul26_C0701
rows.name:
You saved my bacon!
Now how about a buff?

rows.label: soul26_C0702
rows.name:
Us girls gotta stick together!
Buff up!

rows.label: soul26_C0703
rows.name:
Thanks a bunch! Don't forget
your aura, though!

rows.label: soul26_C0801
rows.name:
I may be down, but I'm
gonna knock you out!

rows.label: soul26_C0802
rows.name:
I may be down, but I'm
gonna blast you apart!

rows.label: soul26_C0803
rows.name:
Put me in a corner,
and I always bounce back!

rows.label: soul26_C0901
rows.name:
Man, nice view up here!
Take the shot!

rows.label: soul26_C0902
rows.name: I love a little perspective! Fire!

rows.label: soul26_C0903
rows.name:
I've got the drop on 'em!
Fire away!

rows.label: soul26_C1001
rows.name:
Roll over, Fido!
We're about to get rough!

rows.label: soul26_C1002
rows.name:
And stay down! Now!
They're a sitting duck!

rows.label: soul26_C1003
rows.name:
Down you go!
Let's weaken 'em!

rows.label: soul26_C1101
rows.name:
Smack this punching bag!
They can't even move!

rows.label: soul26_C1102
rows.name:
There's your target!
Gun 'em down!

rows.label: soul26_C1103
rows.name:
Once we weaken 'em,
it's open season!

rows.label: soul26_C1201
rows.name:
They're kinda cute when they're
asleep... But hit 'em anyway!

rows.label: soul26_C1202
rows.name:
Huh, does this count as REM
sleep? Whatever. Shoot 'em!

rows.label: soul26_C1203
rows.name:
Man, I wish I could catch some
Zs! This really burns me up!

rows.label: soul26_C1301
rows.name:
Snagged one!
Come and get 'em!

rows.label: soul26_C1302
rows.name:
Right where I want 'em!
Open fire!

rows.label: soul26_C1303
rows.name:
Anyone looking for
a punching bag?

rows.label: soul26_C1401
rows.name: Wha?! It broke! Patch me up!

rows.label: soul26_C1402
rows.name: I'm okay! Just thwack 'em!

rows.label: soul26_C1403
rows.name:
Somebody shoot that
punk for me!

rows.label: soul26_C1501
rows.name:
Heal me up!
I gotta avenge my Skell!

rows.label: soul26_C1502
rows.name: Damn you! Buff me up!

rows.label: soul26_C1503
rows.name:
Oh my god!
Quick, use Overdrive!

rows.label: soul26_C1601
rows.name:
I got a fuel problem!
Gimme a fix!

rows.label: soul26_C1602
rows.name:
I'm cutting it close here!
Refuel me!

rows.label: soul26_C1603
rows.name:
Can I get a re-up?
I'm really low on fuel!
